{"tid":2267322,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 12 Pro 炒風上揚，金色最多賺 $2,400，256GB 最受歡迎，預期 Pro Max 更好炒！","createTime":"2020-11-02T03:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T08:36:59.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d43bf8e5c95f8df8f0df90800c58fcd8fc57da","tid":2267322,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"上星期iPhone 12及iPhone 12 Pro正式推出，反應比預期更好，iPhone 12 Pro更出現了近年少見的強勢炒風，有價有市。<br />\n<br />\n先達電話店主然哥在出機當日（10月23日）曾預期，iPhone 12 Pro的炒價會在重陽節長假期後，由賺約$1,500至$1,700回落至只賺約$500至$800。但事實卻是機價持續炒上，未見回落，令他大跌眼鏡：「有點意料之外，以今日（10月28日）收市價計，iPhone 12 Pro任何顏色和容量，最少也賺$1,700，最熱門的金色256GB更賺最多，比正價高約$2,400。」<br />\n<br />\n意料之外的，還有今次炒上的顏色和容量，起初大都最看好新的太平洋藍，結果初期依然走勢強勁，但後來卻因放貨太多，收機價有所回落，甚至一度有店舖停收，反而是次選的金色，至今一直少有放貨，供應持續少，價格飆升。「另外，當初我比較看好128GB，但現時卻是256GB最受歡迎。總括來說，我覺得Apple貨量少是最主要的炒高原因。」然哥說。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z-qQBd9aqiA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz-qQBd9aqiA&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=48a1f693\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z-qQBd9aqiA</a>"},{"pid":"ccf1b4a11c38753fa6c048b10c290e36ebac2c40","tid":2267322,"uid":24443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:56:15.000Z","msg":"邊撚個然哥呀 無人識你呀"},{"pid":"429be5341a1b2b6ef7c06f9d8e2fad7a3470a878","tid":2267322,"uid":25619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:56:40.000Z","msg":"炒撚完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693ba3d22af1f231488da49263690d46665f31b3","tid":2267322,"uid":1550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:58:09.000Z","msg":"唔明點解有得炒又運唔到去蝗國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a6286a7c8bbf7121ecf58877c7fec077a254c4","tid":2267322,"uid":38517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"693ba3d22af1f231488da49263690d466